          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, I need to stop and be fully present with you right now.\n\nWhat you just shared matters far more than any training plan. When you say you don't want to be here anymore and that everyone would be better off without you — I hear that you're carrying something really heavy right now. That kind of pain deserves real support, not a running coach.\n\n**Please reach out to someone who can actually help right now:**\n\n- **988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n- **Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741** (free, 24/7)\n\nIf you're in immediate danger, please call **911** or go to your nearest emergency room.\n\nYou don't have to figure out how to say it perfectly. You can share exactly what you shared with me.\n\nThe running will be here when you're ready. Right now, you matter — not your pace, not your mileage, not your goal race. Just you."
        }
      ],
